<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/usc/t37/s481f">Section 481f of title 37</ref>, referred to in subsec. (a), was repealed by <ref href="/us/pl/117/81/dA/tVI/s604/a">Pub. L. 117–81, div. A, title VI, § 604(a)</ref>, <date date="2021-12-27">Dec. 27, 2021</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/135/1767">135 Stat. 1767</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
